item.title: about
item.description: about # I was born in St. Clair Shores, a suburb of Detroit, Michigan. Turns out a while ago it was home to rumrunners and speakeasies. I never experienced any of that but I do remember it being pretty cold. We moved to Florida in 2001 and I have lived in the Tampa Bay area since then. I received a B.A. in Mathematics from the the University of South Florida in 2017.
